Privacy Policy
Overview

This extension is designed with user privacy as a core principle. We do not collect, store, process, or share any personal or non-personal user data.

Data Collection

This extension does not collect any information from users, including but not limited to:

Personal information (such as name, email address, or identifiers)
Usage data
Browsing activity
Device information
Data Storage

This extension does not store any data locally or remotely. No data is written to external servers, databases, or third-party services.

Data Sharing

Since no data is collected or stored, no user data is shared with any third parties under any circumstances.

Permissions

Any permissions requested by the extension are used strictly for its core functionality and not for tracking, data collection, or user profiling.

Third-Party Services

This extension does not use any third-party services, analytics tools, or external APIs that collect or process user data.

Changes to This Policy

If this privacy policy changes in the future, updates will be reflected in this document with a revised "Last Updated" date.

Contact

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please open an issue in the GitHub repository.

